# ZAIKA – Responsive Restaurant Website

A modern and fully responsive restaurant website built to deliver an engaging and visually appealing user experience. The project showcases a clean interface, intuitive navigation, and a mobile-friendly design while demonstrating core front-end development concepts using HTML, CSS, and JavaScript.

## Overview

SavorBite is a static restaurant website designed to provide visitors with an interactive platform to explore the restaurant's menu, services, and contact information. The project emphasizes responsive layouts, modern UI design, and smooth user interactions to create a seamless browsing experience across all devices.

---

## Features

- Responsive design for desktop, tablet, and mobile devices
- Modern and attractive landing page
- Interactive navigation menu
- Food menu with categorized items
- About Us section
- Services section
- Customer testimonials
- Contact section
- Smooth scrolling navigation
- Clean animations and transitions
- User-friendly interface

---

## Technologies Used

- HTML5
- CSS3
- JavaScript

---

## Project Structure

```
SavorBite/
│
├── index.html
│──style.css
├── script.js
└── README.md
```

## Getting Started

Clone the repository

```bash
git clone https://github.com/yourusername/Zaika---Responsive-Restaurant-UI.git
```

Navigate into the project directory

```bash
cd zaika
```

Open `index.html` in your preferred web browser.

